channel.title: Sik-scape 317!
channel.description:
[center]Welcome[/center] this is my project called sik-scape. ive always wanted to make a server and im not very good at coding im very new to it so i ask a lot of help questions. im not the best at making these devlop things but ill try my hardest i just want to say i need hoster (untill i get my vps) admins, mods and a gfx person o and btw i did not leech this but i did not do alot to it as i said im still learning and i hope to be as good as judo or mystic flow or austin or brennan ya u get the point.
